casebody.data:
No. 65,

Orig.

Texas v. New Mexico. [For earlier order herein, see, e. g., 500 U. S. 902.]

Motion of the River Master for approval of fees and expenses granted, and the River Master is awarded $10,705.20 for the period April 1 through June 30, 1991, to be paid equally by the parties. Motion of New Mexico to review the River Master’s final report for Water Year 1990 denied.
